702687f-a.title: Brooklyn: 27th Street (West) - Surf Avenue
702687f-a.text:
West 27th Street, east side, between Surf Ave., and the "Boardwalk",
showing Mc Lochlin's baths, and a series of 1-story bungalows. This view is
north east across East 27th Street, from the "Boardwalk".
August 6, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
